{"tid":1772801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"督察坐女生頭 抱不平街坊被控襲警","createTime":"2019-12-07T03:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T10:02:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":193,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0253e6bcf4320548abc80f13766160c4e55a4d","tid":1772801,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191207/J7QE3K6YVBDUIQOZDROFU3P7MM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191207%2FJ7QE3K6YVBDUIQOZDROFU3P7MM%2F&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=7252f8b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191207%2FJ7QE3K6YVBDUIQOZDROFU3P7MM%2F&h=e742054f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191207/J7QE3K6YVBDUIQOZDROFU3P7MM/</a><br />\n<br />\n督察坐女生頭 抱不平街坊被控襲警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191207/large/1575649014_3f6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575649014_3f6d.jpg&h=7360d172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本月4日，一名便衣女督察將14歲被捕女生的頭「當凳坐」。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本月初有學生疑在土瓜灣快閃堵路，警員派員到場喬裝蒙面埋伏，並且拘捕四名中學生。其間有女督察將14歲被捕女生按在地上將女生的頭「當凳坐」，一名中年男街坊見狀干涉，警方指控他欲上前救人兼打女督察，當場拘捕他，並控以襲警罪。案件昨在九龍城裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n報稱吊車技術員的被告黃偉賢（47歲）被指於本月4日，在土瓜灣馬頭圍道及農圃道交界，襲擊一名執行職務的督察。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉案警無名無代號<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：飛行服務隊 懲教 受累評分跌<br />\n<br />\n控罪書並無透露涉案督察的姓名及編號，亦沒有如近期示威案般使用代號。被告昨被警方押送往法庭，其妻到庭旁聽。散庭後，被告在聲援者掩護下離開法院。案件押後至明年1月17日再訊，待警調查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，控方案情指，事發時現場有人群聚集，其間警方拘捕，一名戴口罩的便衣女督察制服一名學生時，稱遭被告襲擊。女督察事後報稱眼部瘀傷，但傷勢輕微，不需留醫。署理主任裁判官嚴舜儀批准被告保釋候訊，除了本月8日至15日離港旅遊外，其餘日子不得離境。嚴官又下令被告獲保釋至外遊期間，須提交兩萬元保釋金，返港後可調低至2,000元。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC2865/19"},{"pid":"943b8e360b230461e0f1158772cfd610aba50eae","tid":1772801,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f27cc62626a31c94e569a12975552db831fa35","tid":1772801,"uid":13936,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"黑警 = 皇帝"},{"pid":"b9bf1b9d3b9272c2b601eb1368a8f52ab3ef64c3","tid":1772801,"uid":65449,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"乜都冇邊個知你係狗？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGH4Cg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGH4Cg3.jpg&h=592583da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQXoSQo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQXoSQo.jpg&h=d03658d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7M2POoK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7M2POoK.jpg&h=79341225&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdMQxQp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdMQxQp.jpg&h=630a05e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5MUe3L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5MUe3L.jpg&h=bef32859&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pd78jvr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpd78jvr.jpg&h=288a7a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SLyjras.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSLyjras.jpg&h=b9005126&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NusgtoN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNusgtoN.jpg&h=1213b2c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4SgtoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4SgtoO.jpg&h=38e3565b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w1Y7z3O.jpg\" data-